{
  "stem": "1641.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he was, of course, doing it together with him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So every day, he took  down two-- two boys, three boys, two in the morning, two in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they came back with terrible pains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- they-- they put some pus into their arms and in the-- in their legs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We don't know what-- what he put in, but it must have been terribly painful.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And other boys had to swallow four yellow tablets every hour, and they developed malaria, huge, high temperatures, and all sorts of diseases.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we-- he didn't give us the details what he did, but there were-- there were people all crying all night and, ooh, you know, in terrible pains.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This went on like that for weeks and weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a-- a Polish doctor, a Polish Christian doctor, who was there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was trying to help us and give us what he could.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sometimes he could get some aspirin for the pain, not always, but he-- he did his best.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was-- he was very helpful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I had long discussions with him, because that was the time when the Warsaw uprising, not the Jewish uprising.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was the previous year.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was the-- the Christian uprising of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we even-- we discussed military position in Warsaw, how the fights is going on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And later on this friendship was very important for me, because he saved my life later on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But anyhow, eventually the day came when they called me out, and that was the last experiment of this series.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And to my colossal good luck, all he did is I had to lie on my stomach, and I got a slight ether-- so a bit-- a bits put to sleep almost.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
